    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "- Do we need it? Yes we need it, for usage beyond the web (for example using react-native)\n- Does it leak? as far as I can tell no. One of the of props of `InstantSearch` let you pass your own implementation, while theoretically nice to have, I don't know why we would and I suggest we remove it if we're not sure :) \n",
