    "body": "> One of the of props of InstantSearch let you pass your own implementation, while theoretically nice to have, I don't know why we would and I suggest we remove it if we're not sure :)\n\nIt seems to be the way to make IS + React-Router work together, we will see how it goes with #1239 \n",
